00:49:59.808 --> 00:50:02.170
I'm trying to understand
your question.

00:50:02.170 --> 00:50:04.240
- So instead of having,
now, this antenna, which

00:50:04.240 --> 00:50:06.870
maps through all frequencies,
to say I don't know,

00:50:06.870 --> 00:50:10.260
like from this capacity
to this capacity,

00:50:10.260 --> 00:50:11.700
it's going to be this note.

00:50:11.700 --> 00:50:14.760
And I'm only going to have
a specific chromatic scale

00:50:14.760 --> 00:50:16.480
or something that
